content: Hello, I just got a phone call from someone who wants to donate to Kamala Harris via phone. Is there a phone number he can call to donate? <#1242256751445934262> <#1263529508300914809>
<@892601853873905697> they can donate from https://secure.actblue.com/donate/web-hfp-october-01-2024?refcode=hfp_menu&opt_id=oeu1725030782633r0.6119725332065697 on their mobile browser.
For whateer reason, he doesn't want to use an online form.  He prefers to give someone his credit card info over the phone.

They can write a check and send it to.
https://kamalaharris.com/donate-by-mail/
Sorry, I can't find a phone number. which is understandable, because folks could call them and talk about all sorts of things instead of donate.
